thread.title_full: Aussie Vac @ Ducted Vacuum Centre reviewed by Suz

author: Suz
title: Suz
text: These guys are awesome! Despite lack of predictability about delivery dates through Australia Post, I received my order within a couple of days which was awesome. Great when you have a ducted vac system and know what you want - can also phone and discuss if unsure. Highly recommended!!
